Spain Leaves Door Open for More Tax Increases, Expansion Says

-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 
2011-05-02T07:15:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/spain-leaves-door-open-for-more-tax-increases-expansion-says.html
Spanish government left open the
possibility of further tax increases aimed at avoiding new
spending cuts,  Expansion  reported, citing a stability program
sent to the European Commission.  The government may approve the measure after local and
regional elections on May 22, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
